# OGFN

This project is divided into different categories to keep content and components better organized.

## Categories

- Launcher
- Backends
- Build Archive
- Gameservers
- Launchers
- Packs

## Overview

- Launcher: Entry point for using the content
  - Source: [Launcher](Launcher/)
- Backends: Server-side components and services
  - Source: [Backends](Backends/)
- Build Archive: Archived build versions
  - Source: [Build Archive](Build%20Archive/)
- Gameservers: Game server and hosting components
  - Source: [Gameservers](Gameservers/)
- Launchers: Launcher files and configurations
  - Source: [Launchers](Launchers/)
- Packs: Packaged content and resources
  - Source: [Packs](Packs/)

## Folder Structure

- [Backends](Backends/) - Source
- [Build Archive](Build%20Archive/) - Source
- [Gameservers](Gameservers/) - Source
- [Launchers](Launchers/) - Source
- [Packs](Packs/) - Source

